title: 22 — Enterable Objects
story: regression
author: Sharpee Regression Suite
description: Verify EnterableTrait — enter and exit a maintenance booth

---

# Examine the booth
> examine booth
[OK: contains "booth"]

# Enter the booth
> enter booth
[OK: contains_any "enter" "get in" "booth" "inside"]

# Exit the booth
> exit booth
[OK: contains_any "exit" "get out" "leave" "booth" "Control Room"]
